Prismatic solid shapes (also called prismoids) can be created with [[Image:Part_Extrude.svg|16px]] [[Part_Extrude|Part Extrude]], too if the option {{MenuCommand|Create solid}} is checked, or with [[Image:PartDesign_Pad.svg|16px]] [[PartDesign_Pad|PartDesign Pad]].
